Same problem here, looking at the Riot logs("C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\LeagueClient Logs\2017-12-05xxxx_LeagueClient.log") it seems to be an SSL issue: ALE-4FBFEF56 - CONNECT_FAILED - {"message":"SSL_ERROR_SYSCALL - The underlying BIO reported an I/O error.","errorCode_int":5} 

Tried reinstalling / hextech / reboot and nothing seems to be working. 

There are people saying to try using a vpn like hotspot shield or something to fix it but thats too much work to play a game :D
